Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.47,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}E então, houveram encontros que me trouxeram até o presente.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Atirem!
